00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:44,239
But given his current situation,

727
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:48,079
how old will you be when he pulls through?

728
00:37:48,559 --> 00:37:49,599
And when he does pull through,

729
00:37:49,599 --> 00:37:50,880
what if his feelings change?

730
00:37:51,199 --> 00:37:52,239
It's too big of a variable.

731
00:37:52,239 --> 00:37:54,440
Mom, you're thinking too far.

732
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:56,039
This is just a job.

733
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,809
My relationship with Hou Jue is just work-related.

734
00:37:59,769 --> 00:38:01,360
That's enough. You've gotten way off track.

735
00:38:01,679 --> 00:38:03,119
Stop talking. He'll be back soon.

736
00:38:03,519 --> 00:38:04,519
So what if he comes back?

737
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:06,119
I dare say this even if he's here.

738
00:38:06,769 --> 00:38:07,769
I'm telling you.

739
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:10,159
We're not the ones being disloyal. He is.

740
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,960
How could he? He has lost his footing.

741
00:38:12,119 --> 00:38:13,440
And he is dragging you down along with him.

742
00:38:13,599 --> 00:38:15,119
Is this what a man should do?

743
00:38:15,809 --> 00:38:16,920
Mom, you...

744
00:38:19,639 --> 00:38:21,119
This is so frustrating.

745
00:38:21,119 --> 00:38:22,119
Ms. Zhang, you're here.

746
00:38:25,079 --> 00:38:27,719
Shi Yi, I just ordered lunch and dinner.

747
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:29,039
Hang in there for one more day.

748
00:38:29,329 --> 00:38:30,360
You don't need to eat this tomorrow.

749
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,480
Ms. Zhang, have some water.

750
00:38:33,599 --> 00:38:34,599
I don't want any.

751
00:38:34,599 --> 00:38:35,599
I have to go.

752
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,360
Hou Jue.

753
00:38:39,809 --> 00:38:41,039
Aren't you going to see me out?

754
00:38:42,719 --> 00:38:44,000
Yes. I'll be right there.

755
00:38:44,639 --> 00:38:45,639
Mom.

756
00:38:46,079 --> 00:38:47,239
Just stay here.

757
00:38:47,239 --> 00:38:48,809
I just want a few words with Hou Jue.

758
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,599
What do you want to say?

759
00:39:07,599 --> 00:39:08,599
Hou Jue.

760
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:10,289
Let's sit here and talk.

761
00:39:10,519 --> 00:39:11,519
Okay.

762
00:39:17,679 --> 00:39:18,920
First of all, I should thank you.

763
00:39:18,920 --> 00:39:19,920
You've been taking care of Shi Yi.

764
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:21,599
I can see she is recovering well.

765
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:24,239
It's nothing. Shi Yi has always been fit.

766
00:39:24,239 --> 00:39:25,239
I don't need to do much.

767
00:39:25,769 --> 00:39:26,960
No matter how fit you are,

768
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:29,289
after 30, your body starts going downhill.

769
00:39:29,599 --> 00:39:30,639
She's stronger than most people.

770
00:39:30,769 --> 00:39:32,400
She can take down 4 or 5 of me.

771
00:39:32,840 --> 00:39:34,159
Those words don't sit well with me.

772
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:37,920
Is a girl being better than others at something like that a good thing?

773
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:41,559
You're right. It's not that good.

774
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:46,000
I called you here...

775
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,199
to tell you...

776
00:39:48,559 --> 00:39:51,039
that Shi Yi has done more than enough for you.

777
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:53,719
She almost died a few days ago.

778
00:39:53,719 --> 00:39:54,809
Although she doesn't think that way,

779
00:39:54,809 --> 00:39:56,119
that's how I feel.

780
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,639
Ms. Zhang, I certainly won't forget...

781
00:39:59,639 --> 00:40:00,840
how Shi Yi saved me.

782
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:03,199
Whether you forget it or not is not important.

783
00:40:04,199 --> 00:40:05,880
Actually, when she got hurt last time,

784
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:07,079
I wanted to come to find you.

785
00:40:07,360 --> 00:40:08,360
But then I thought...

786
00:40:08,809 --> 00:40:11,289
she's just accomplishing a mission under a contract.

787
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:12,599
It's not your fault.

788
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:13,920
So I didn't go.

789
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:19,159
Actually, she got hurt because of me.

790
00:40:19,809 --> 00:40:20,809
I'm responsible.

791
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:21,920
Yes.

792
00:40:22,809 --> 00:40:25,239
That's why with one thing leading after another,

793
00:40:25,239 --> 00:40:26,639
I feel anxious.

794
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:29,289
With her condition now,

795
00:40:29,289 --> 00:40:30,440
even after she is discharged,

796
00:40:30,599 --> 00:40:32,039
it'll take some time for her to recover.

797
00:40:32,329 --> 00:40:34,360
After all, she had surgery, right?

798
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:36,920
Right now,

799
00:40:37,329 --> 00:40:38,719
you don't have any income.

800
00:40:39,329 --> 00:40:41,039
You even have to pay Shi Yi's wages.

801
00:40:41,519 --> 00:40:42,960
Actually,

802
00:40:44,239 --> 00:40:45,920
it's a heavy burden to you too.

803
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,480
It just so happens...

804
00:40:48,599 --> 00:40:49,599
that there's someone...

805
00:40:50,559 --> 00:40:52,480
who can take care of Shi Yi better than you right now.

806
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,960
He can give Shi Yi everything she needs.

807
00:40:56,329 --> 00:40:58,079
As Shi Yi's good friend,

808
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:00,519
what should you do?

809
00:41:05,119 --> 00:41:07,840
So Shi Yi found a new job. Is that right?

810
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:10,559
Let's just say that.

811
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:13,960
Who is it?

812
00:41:15,559 --> 00:41:16,559
Lan Qi.

813
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:17,840
You've met him.

814
00:41:19,119 --> 00:41:20,119
Yes.

815
00:41:20,960 --> 00:41:21,960
This child...

816
00:41:22,199 --> 00:41:23,329
is talented and successful.

817
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:24,960
He has a good career too.

818
00:41:25,329 --> 00:41:27,599
He had a relationship with Shi Yi in the past too.

819
00:41:29,119 --> 00:41:31,440
He can offer Shi Yi better working conditions.

820
00:41:32,769 --> 00:41:33,769
What's important is...

821
00:41:34,159 --> 00:41:36,119
it's an easy job and there's no danger.

822
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:39,159
Moreover, it can maximize Shi Yi's value.